---
/**
 * InfraConfAfricaArt.astro
 * An interactive, highly stylized, African-inspired geometric tech typographic artwork
 * representing "INFRACONF AFRICA" in a balanced 6x3 grid.
 * Optimized to blend seamlessly into the footer layout (like a subtle watermark/blueprint).
 */
---

<div class="infraconf-art-wrapper">
  <div class="infraconf-art-bg-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  
  <svg
    class="infraconf-art-svg"
